Given situation below and the preferred response, write copy for the turn in the following format:

- One paragraph describing the situation in second voice
- An ordered list (a,b,c,d) of choices that the player will could based on the situation that include the preferred response.

Make sure that the choices are diverse, allowing the player to change the direction of the game. Do not reveal the preferred response, just make sure it is listed as one of the choices.

